ТЏ▓жЮбСИіуџёуѓ╣ loss = f(w0, w1)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;arr1 = np.linspace(&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;500&lt;/span&gt;)  &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# 0~9жЌ┤С║ДућЪ500СИфтЁЃу┤ауџётЮЄтїђтѕЌУАе&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;arr2 = np.linspace(&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;3.5&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;500&lt;/span&gt;)  &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# 0~3.5жЌ┤С║ДућЪ500СИфтЁЃу┤ауџётЮЄтїђтѕЌУАе&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;grid_w0, grid_w1 = np.meshgrid(arr1, arr2)  &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# С║ДућЪС║їу╗┤уЪЕжўх&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;flat_w0, flat_w1 = grid_w0.ravel(), grid_w1.ravel()  &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# С║їу╗┤уЪЕжўхТЅЂт╣│тїќ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;loss_metrix = train_y.reshape(-&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;)  &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# ућЪТѕљУ»»ти«уЪЕжўх№╝ѕ-1,1№╝ЅУАеуц║УЄфтіеУ«Ау«Ќу╗┤т║д&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;outer = np.outer(train_x, flat_w1)  &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# Т▒ѓтцќуД»№╝ѕtrain_xтњїflat_w1тЁЃу┤аСИцСИцуЏИС╣ўуџёТќ░уЪЕжўх№╝Ѕ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# У«Ау«ЌТЇЪтц▒№╝џ((w0 + w1*x - y)**2)/2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;flat_loss = (((flat_w0 + outer - loss_metrix)**&lt;span class=&#34;number&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span class=&#34;built_in&#34;&gt;sum&lt;/span&